  { question: `Should I use Copilot or Claude for coding from India?`, answer: `Both, in different roles. Copilot for in-editor autocomplete and quick chat. Claude (or ChatGPT) for architectural conversations and complex multi-file refactors. Cursor and Claude Code blur the line; pick based on workflow preference.` },
  { question: `Does Copilot leak my company's code?`, answer: `By default, Pro plan does not train on your code. Business plan has stricter contractual data protection. For sensitive enterprise work, the Business plan is the safe default.` },
